Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.82,main,FOX,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay up all night chatting, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:22.04,main,FOX,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us all about your youthful troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:25.68,main,OLMAR,0000,0000,0000,,You're hoping I'll entertain you \Nwhile you drink, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.54,main,OLMAR,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this. I'm going home. Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:32.96,main,FOX,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Tell us everything \Nthat's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.93,main,FOX,0000,0000,0000,,We're such good friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.32,main,OLMAR,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell we are. Let go.
